# Implementation Plan: Dashboards, Bookings & Admin Verifications

We will implement the complete workflow for super admin registrations, doctor verification, paginated/filtered dashboards, and double-booking prevention. Clinical records (prescriptions/reports) have been omitted per your instructions.

---

## Logic Critique & Corrections

### 1. Delete vs. Cancel Appointments
* **Adjustment:** Instead of a hard database delete which breaks historical logs, the `Delete Appointment` request will set the appointment's `EAppointmentStatus` to `Cancelled`.

### 2. Double-Booking Overlap Validation
When booking an appointment at a specific time:
* The system checks that the **Doctor** has no other appointment at the same date and time interval.
* The system checks that the **Patient** has no other appointment at the same date and time interval.

